// カスタムアイコンコンポーネント
const RakutenIcon = () => (
  <Box component="span" sx={{ 
    width: 20, 
    height: 20, 
    display: 'inline-block',
    background: 'url("/icons/rakuten.png") no-repeat center',
    backgroundSize: 'contain',
    mr: 0.5
  }} />
);

const YahooIcon = () => (
  <Box component="span" sx={{ 
    width: 20, 
    height: 20, 
    display: 'inline-block',
    background: 'url("/icons/yahoo.png") no-repeat center',
    backgroundSize: 'contain',
    mr: 0.5
  }} />
);

const UsedIcon = () => (
  <Box component="span" sx={{ 
    width: 20, 
    height: 20, 
    display: 'inline-block',
    background: 'url("/icons/used.png") no-repeat center',
    backgroundSize: 'contain',
    mr: 0.5
  }} />
);

export default function ClubRecommendations() {
  const [category, setCategory] = useState('driver');

  const handleCategoryChange = (event, newValue) => {
    setCategory(newValue);
  };

  return (
    <Box sx={{ width: '100%', height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
      {/* カテゴリタブ */}
      <Box sx={{ borderBottom: 1, borderColor: 'divider', mb: 2 }}>
        <Tabs
          value={category}
          onChange={handleCategoryChange}
          variant="scrollable"
          scrollButtons="auto"
          sx={{
            '& .MuiTab-root': {
              fontWeight: 600,
              fontSize: 15,
              minWidth: 100,
              color: '#666',
              '&.Mui-selected': { color: '#111' }
            },
            '& .MuiTabs-indicator': {
              height: 3,
              background: '#111'
            }
          }}
        >
          <Tab label="ドライバー" value="driver" />
          <Tab label="ウッド" value="wood" />
          <Tab label="アイアン" value="iron" />
          <Tab label="ウェッジ" value="wedge" />
          <Tab label="パター" value="putter" />
        </Tabs>
      </Box>

      {/* 商品一覧 */}
      <Box sx={{ flex: 1, overflowY: 'auto', px: 1 }}>
        {clubData[category].map((club) => (
          <motion.div
            key={club.id}
            initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
            animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
            transition={{ duration: 0.3 }}
          >
            <Paper
              elevation={2}
              sx={{
                p: 2,
                mb: 2,
                borderRadius: 2,
                '&:hover': {
                  boxShadow: 4,
                  transform: 'translateY(-2px)',
                  transition: 'all 0.2s'
                }
              }}
            >
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2 }}>
                {/* 商品画像 */}
                <Avatar
                  src={club.image}
                  alt={club.name}
                  sx={{ width: 100, height: 100, borderRadius: 2 }}
                />

                {/* 商品情報 */}
                <Box sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
                  {/* ヘッダー部分 */}
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'flex-start', mb: 1.5 }}>
                    <Box>
                      <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, mb: 0.5 }}>{club.name}</Typography>
                      <Typography variant="subtitle2" color="text.secondary">
                        {club.maker} | {club.specs}
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                    <Chip
                      label={`マッチ度 ${club.match}%`}
                      color="primary"
                      size="small"
                      sx={{ fontWeight: 600 }}
                    />
                  </Box>

                  {/* マッチ理由 */}
                  <Typography 
                    variant="body2" 
                    color="text.secondary" 
                    sx={{ 
                      mb: 1.5,
                      backgroundColor: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03)',
                      p: 1,
                      borderRadius: 1,
                      fontSize: '0.875rem'
                    }}
                  >
                    {club.matchReason}
                  </Typography>

                  {/* レビュー */}
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 1.5 }}>
                    <Rating value={club.rating} precision={0.1} size="small" readOnly />
                    <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ ml: 1 }}>
                      {club.reviews}件のレビュー
                    </Typography>
                  </Box>

                  {/* 価格表示 */}
                  <Box sx={{ 
                    mb: 2,
                    display: 'flex',
                    alignItems: 'baseline',
                    gap: 2
                  }}>
                    <Box>
                      <Typography variant="caption" color="text.secondary" sx={{ display: 'block' }}>
                        新品価格
                      </Typography>
                      <Typography variant="h6" color="primary" sx={{ fontWeight: 700 }}>
                        ¥{club.price.toLocaleString()}
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                    <Box>
                      <Typography variant="caption" color="text.secondary" sx={{ display: 'block' }}>
                        中古価格
                      </Typography>
                      <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'baseline', gap: 1 }}>
                        <Typography variant="h6" color="success.main" sx={{ fontWeight: 700 }}>
                          ¥{(club.price * 0.6).toLocaleString()}
                        </Typography>
                        <Chip
                          label="40%OFF"
                          size="small"
                          color="success"
                          sx={{ height: 20, fontSize: '0.75rem' }}
                        />
                      </Box>
                    </Box>
                  </Box>

                  {/* アクションボタン */}
                  <Box sx={{ 
                    display: 'grid',
                    gridTemplateColumns: 'repeat(4, 1fr)',
                    gap: 1,
                    '& .MuiButton-root': {
                      height: 40,
                      fontSize: '0.875rem',
                      whiteSpace: 'nowrap',
                      textTransform: 'none'
                    }
                  }}>
                    <Button
                      variant="contained"
                      startIcon={<InfoOutlinedIcon />}
                      sx={{
                        bgcolor: '#111',
                        color: '#fff',
                        '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#222' }
                      }}
                    >
                      詳細を確認
                    </Button>
                    <Button
                      variant="outlined"
                      startIcon={<RakutenIcon />}
                      href={club.rakutenUrl}
                      target="_blank"
                      sx={{
                        borderColor: '#E91E63',
                        color: '#E91E63',
                        '&:hover': { borderColor: '#C2185B', bgcolor: '#FCE4EC' }
                      }}
                    >
                      楽天で購入
                    </Button>
                    <Button
                      variant="outlined"
                      startIcon={<YahooIcon />}
                      href={club.yahooUrl}
                      target="_blank"
                      sx={{
                        borderColor: '#FF9800',
                        color: '#FF9800',
                        '&:hover': { borderColor: '#F57C00', bgcolor: '#FFF3E0' }
                      }}
                    >
                      Yahoo!で購入
                    </Button>
                    <Button
                      variant="outlined"
                      startIcon={<UsedIcon />}
                      href={club.usedUrl}
                      target="_blank"
                      sx={{
                        borderColor: '#4CAF50',
                        color: '#4CAF50',
                        '&:hover': { borderColor: '#388E3C', bgcolor: '#E8F5E9' }
                      }}
                    >
                      中古を探す
                    </Button>
                  </Box>
                </Box>
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </motion.div>
        ))}
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}
